name: Dark Wonder
description: Nothing is more mysterious than a storm at night. What’s out there?  What’s happening? All you know is what the storm will show you, the giants fighting in the clouds. If it’s far enough, you can’t hear the thunder. You hear crickets and night sounds while the heavens blaze away, you feel only the wind on your cheek. Swing away, higher, up into the night sky. Get some popcorn. It's a FINAL moment of wonder.
